Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Master of Radiance level 1.
Specifics: At each level, the Master of Radiance progresses in one selected divine spellcasting class. If a character had more than one spellcasting class in which she could cast spells before she became a Master of Radiance, the player must decide which class to progress for the purpose of determining spells per day and spells known.
Use: Automatic.